    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#checkingModal">
        <a class="tooltip-multiline tooltip-bottom" data-tooltip="A bank account that allows a customer to deposit and withdraw money and write checks. Using a checking account can be safer and more convenient than handling cash.
